Kingdom of Gladiators II: The Tournament | Full Movie | Action Fantasy Movie

A Templar Knight is forced to fight as a gladiator where challengers from different worlds duel in a quest for a magical sword. Then the Templar learns he is scheduled to fight his master who has become a man of greed and ambition.

2017.  Stars: Danielle Kamela, Greg Maness, Solofa Fatu Jr.
